# Työvuorolista Marketing Website

## Project Overview
This is the marketing website for Työvuorolista, a shift scheduling application for Finnish businesses. The site is built with Astro and deployed on Vercel.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Astro 2.5.7
- **UI Library**: React 18.2.0 (via @astrojs/react)
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Deployment**: Vercel (serverless)
- **Email Service**: AWS SES
- **Internationalization**: Built-in Astro i18n (Finnish, English, Swedish)

## Project Structure
- `src/pages/` - Astro pages and routes
- `src/components/` - React and Astro components
- `src/i18n/` - Translation files (fi.json, en.json, sv.json)
- `src/layouts/` - Page layouts
- `api/` - API endpoints (handleForm.mjs, handleUnsubscribe.mjs)
- `public/` - Static assets (images, videos)

## Key Features
- Multi-language support (Finnish default, English, Swedish)
- Blog posts (markdown files in src/pages/posts/)
- Contact form integration
- Email subscription/unsubscription
- Industry-specific landing pages
- Responsive design

## API Endpoints
- `/api/handleForm` - Contact form submission (AWS SES)
- `/api/handleUnsubscribe` - Email unsubscription

## Development
- Run: `npm run dev`
- Build: `npm run build`
- Preview: `npm run preview`

## Important Notes
- Default locale is Finnish (no prefix)
- English and Swedish use `/en/` and `/sv/` prefixes
- Site URL: https://www.tyovuorolista.fi/
- Trailing slashes are disabled
